This paper proposes an active learning approach for transferring representations across domains, which is a common problem in computer vision and machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on domain adaptation and transfer learning, which are subfields of machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
